— (2003). "Mirror reflections: fundamentalism and the market economy". openDemocracy Ltd. {{cite journal}}: Cite journal requires |journal= (help)
— (October 2006). "A comparison of the Viable System Model and Seven Models of Risk with the effects of the Sarbanes-Oxley legislation". Journal of Organisational Transformation and Social Change. 3 (1).
— (2007). "Clues from a clownfish: ten ideas for a better world". openDemocracy Ltd. {{cite journal}}: Cite journal requires |journal= (help)

